<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="envy-n">envy <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'envi/    美 /'envi/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>妒忌；羡慕；羡慕对象 / 目标：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Lucky you — I'm <strong>green with envy</strong>!
你可真幸运——我都有点嫉妒了(眼红了)！</p><footer>外研⑦ – 5</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He couldn't hide his <strong>envy of</strong> me.
他遮掩不住对我的妒忌。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I felt <strong>envy at / of</strong> his success. 
我羡慕他的成功。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-the-envy-of">be the envy of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>是令…羡慕或嫉妒的对象</strong>  </p></div>